KID 1: Oh. he moves it!
He moves it!

1748
02:00:53.163 --> 02:00:54.825
KID 2: Who man is that?
KID 3: Bucket!

1749
02:00:54.998 --> 02:00:55.988
KID 2: Easy.

1750
02:00:59.002 --> 02:01:00.334
When you said
you would take me

1751
02:01:00.420 --> 02:01:02.332
