our knowledge and resources...</i>

1795
02:05:40.950 --> 02:05:42.816
<i>with the outside world.</i>

1796
02:05:42.994 --> 02:05:46.362
<i>Wakanda will no longer
watch from the shadows.</i>

1797
02:05:46.539 --> 02:05:47.950
<i>We cannot.</i>

1798
02:05:49.083 --> 02:05:50.574
<i>We must not.</i>

1799
02:05:50.918 --> 02:05:53.535
<i>We will work to be an example
of how we...</i>

1800
02:05:53.713 --> 02:05:55.955
<i>as brothers and sisters
on this earth...</i>

1801
02:05:56.132 --> 02:05:58.169
<i>should treat each other.</i>

1802
02:05:58.342 --> 02:06:00.174
<i>Now. more than ever...</i>

1803
02:06:01.429 --> 02:06:05.844
<i>the illusions of division
threaten our very existence.</i>

1804
02:06:06.267 --> 02:06:08.179
<i>We all know the truth.</i>

1805
02:06:08.352 --> 02:06:11.766
<i>More connects us
than separates us.</i>

1806
02:06:11.939 --> 02:06:13.646
<i>But in times of crisis...</i>

1807
02:06:13.816 --> 02:06:16.274
<i>the wise build bridges...</i>

1808
02:06:16.444 --> 02:06:19.232
<i>while the foolish
build barriers.</i>

1809
02:06:19.405 --> 02:06:21.442
<i>We must find a way...</i>

1810
02:06:21.616 --> 02:06:24.233
<i>to look after one another...</i>

1811
02:06:24.410 --> 02:06:29.121
<i>as if we were one.
single tribe.</i>

1812
02:06:29.290 --> 02:06:30.747
<i>With all due respect.
King T'Challa...</i>

1813
02:06:30.917 --> 02:06:32.158
<i>what can a nation of farmers</i>

1814
02:06:32.251 --> 02:06:34.117
<i>have to offer
the rest of the world?</i>

1815
02:06:34.545 --> 02:06:36.036
(ALL MURMURING)

1816
02:13:26.582 --> 02:13:28.244
(RUSTLES)

1817
02:13:30.252 --> 02:13:31.914
(BOYS GIGGLING)

1818
02:13:33.714 --> 02:13:35.706
Are you playing around
with that man again?

1819
02:13:35.799 --> 02:13:36.789
- No.
- You're teasing him again.

1820
02:13:38.219 --> 02:13:40.336
- Don't wake him. He must rest.
- THABO: No. I'm not.

1821
02:13:41.305 --> 02:13:42.671
No. I'm not.

1822
02:13:43.641 --> 02:13:44.848
SHURI: Thabo.
you're doing that.

1823
02:13:45.017 --> 02:13:46.383
KID 2: He's doing it.
He's lying.

1824
02:13:46.560 --> 02:13:47.971
SHURI: No. he's resting.

1825
02:13:48.270 --> 02:13:49.477
Go. go!

1826
02:13:49.647 --> 02:13:51.434
KIDS: (IN XHOSA) White Wolf!

1827
02:13:51.565 --> 02:13:52.601
SHURI: (IN ENGLISH) Stop that!

1828
02:13:52.733 --> 02:13:53.849
KIDS: (IN XHOSA) White Wolf!

1829
02:13:56.612 --> 02:13:58.228
(IN ENGLISH)
Good morning. Sergeant Barnes.

1830
02:13:59.740 --> 02:14:00.730
Bucky.

1831
02:14:02.368 --> 02:14:03.404
How are you feeling?

1832
02:14:04.036 --> 02:14:05.026
Good.

1833
02:14:07.665 --> 02:14:08.746
Thank you.

1834
02:14:08.832 --> 02:14:10.368
(CHUCKLES SOFTLY) Come.

1835
02:14:11.877 --> 02:14:13.743
Much more for you to learn.
